                    <span>This is the best book I have ever read!  I read it over and over! A must read!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Easy to learn, easy to retain, easy to enjoy :)</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>37</span>
